author: Nickarama
title: OOPS! Chelsea Clinton Tries to Be Clever, but Ends Up Embarrassing Her Family In a Serious Way…
text:
Do you like this article? 
Chelsea Clinton hasn’t quite figured out Twitter yet. 
It’s sort of like the old lawyer maxim: never ask a question to which you don’t know the answer. 
Ivy League-educated Chelsea couldn’t figure out a word she needed. 
So she asked Merriam Webster and Twitter: what was an unsuccessful troll called? 
Merriam Webster did try to help. 
But needless to say, it didn’t go well. Some people had great answers for Chelsea’s question: what was an unsuccessful troll called? 
Bam! 
Chelsea isn’t any better at Twitter than her mother is at winning elections. 
When your parents are Bill and Hillary Clinton, there’s just too much ammunition. 
Back out now, Chelsea…
